<div class="full-bleed grey" id="about">
  <div class="sec-eyebrow">About Me</div>
  <div class="sec-title">The person behind the content.</div>
  <p class="sec-sub">A creative thinker who bridges the gap between technology and human storytelling.</p>
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-text">
      <p>I'm Divyanshi — a content writer and digital strategist with a deep interest in how AI is reshaping the way we communicate.</p>
      <p>Currently a <strong>Junior Content Creator</strong> at <strong>Aadhunik.ai</strong> and <strong>Sociobits</strong>, I specialise in simplifying complex tech narratives into stories that resonate across blogs, social, and brand campaigns.</p>
      <p>I completed my studies in <strong>Mass Media & Communication (BAMMC)</strong> at <strong>Thakur College of Science and Commerce</strong>, which sharpened my instincts for advertising, brand storytelling, and audience-first thinking.</p>
      <p>Looking for: <span class="grad-word">Marketing · Copywriting · Digital Marketing · Content Strategy Internships</span></p>
    </div>
